transactionHash.description: 合约调用成功后返回的：transactionHash

userOperationHash.description: 合约调用成功后返回的：userOpsHash

paymasterAndData.description: Address of paymaster sponsoring the transaction, followed by extra data to send to the paymaster (empty for self-sponsored transaction)

callGasLimit.description: The amount of gas to allocate the main execution call

initCode.description: The initCode of the account (needed if and only if the account is not yet on-chain and needs to be created)

signature.description: Data passed into the account along with the nonce during the verification step

callData.description: The data to pass to the sender during the main execution call

verificationGasLimit.description: The amount of gas to allocate for the verification step

maxPriorityFeePerGas.description: Maximum priority fee per gas (similar to EIP-1559 max_priority_fee_per_gas)

maxFeePerGas.description: Maximum fee per gas (similar to EIP-1559 max_fee_per_gas)

preVerificationGas.description: The amount of gas to pay for to compensate the bundler for pre-verification execution, calldata and any gas overhead that can’t be tracked on-chain

post.description: 前端监听到合约成功事件，调用加快后端事件处理
get paymaster and data by user operation
